  "notes": "Standalone defensive structure built anywhere, not tied to a base. Clears fog of war at a wide radius independent of its attack range. Comes in several material variants that play differently rather than a flat cost/power tradeoff: one favors high damage and slow fire, one trades damage for rapid fire and gains an extra independently-targeting turret per upgrade for clearing swarms, and one drops air targeting but adds flat damage reduction, the highest health, and splash damage for soaking and clearing ground pushes. Also doubles as a stealth detector, though its detection radius is much shorter than its normal vision range. A destroyed tower disappears outright rather than leaving a discounted ruin to rebuild from.",

